headline: Jobs report, consumer credit, Summer Games Fest: What to Watch
summary: Market Domination Overtime hosts Julie Hyman and Josh Lipton preview the top market stories and headlines Wall Street will be paying attention to tomorrow, Friday, June 6, including the May jobs report, April's consumer credit reading, and the 2025 Summer Games Fest kicks off, where many video game developers like Sony (SONY), Microsoft (MSFT), and Nintendo (NTDOY, 7974.T) will be in attendance. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime here.
